                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-215-off1220 t18240114-215-cd1221"></join>, a handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240114-215-victim1860" type="victimName">
